## Summary
This pull request includes the implementation of a simple dashboard page within the go-orca codebase that displays in-flight workflows and allows users to submit new ones. The implementation uses existing API endpoints (GET /workflows and POST /workflows) and adheres to architectural simplicity by using only one HTML page and one JS file.

## Testing
The quality gate requires running `go test ./...` until all tests are passing. After executing the command, all unit tests passed successfully.

```
go test ./...
ok      github.com/gorca/go-orca 0.512s
```